<h3>As part of a successful green card application, <a href="https://www.boundless.com/">Boundless Immigration</a> needs to collect dozens of difficult-to-obtain documents from customers.</h3>
<h5>The process can take some customers weeks or months to complete. Moreover, a Boundless team member needs to look at every single uploaded document. We had a backlog of <span style="color:$red">20,000 documents</span><sup>1</sup> that werenâ€™t budging.</h5>

